   On the Net:
</P>
<P>
   National Rifle Association: http://www.nra.org
</P>
<P>
   Connecticut attorney general:
http://www.cslnet.ctstateu.edu/attygenl
</P>
<P>
   Smith &AMP; Wesson: http://www.smith-wesson.com
</P>
