Angeles Lakers struggled to a 111-104 win Wednesday night over the woeful Golden
State Warriors. Shaquille O'Neal scored 49 points as the Lakers won their 11th
straight game and clinched homecourt advantage throughout the playoffs. Los
Angeles has won 30 of its last 31 games.
</P>
